public class FeatureServicePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener, javax.swing.event.ListDataListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener, javax.swing.event.ChangeListener, javax.swing.event.TreeSelectionListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener

This class implements the ArcIMS wizard's panel which enables the user to select which layers must be retrieved from a Image Service (selected on the ServiceNamesPanel).

Author:
jldominguez
See Also:
